Move focused window
	left					 + Shift + Left
	right					 + Shift + Right
	up					 + Shift + Up
	down					 + Shift + Down

Scratchpad
	save to					 + Shift+ -
	recall					 + -

Resize						 + r + Left, Right, Up, Down

Change layout
	stacking				 + s
	tabbed					 + w
	toggle split				 + e

Lock screen					 + Shift + x

Brightness:
	increse					 + Ctrl + p
	decrease				 + Ctrl + o

Start programs:
	show/hide calendar			 + Ctrl + d
	file browser				 + Ctrl + f
	midnight commander			 + Ctrl + Return
	take screenshot				Prt Sc
	terminal				 + Return
	text editor				 + Ctrl + t
	internet browser			 + Ctrl + b